channel.title: F2P pkz my first server please look
channel.description:
I made everything from combat to the bank screens, so please take a look
Work time on this server 3 weeks Hi im mr arrows
and this is my first server
Its based off of real Free to play runescape
Its not completely FTP but mostly it has a small amount of dragon items
You start out with 99 strength 40 atk 1 def 99 RANGE 1 prayer 99 magic
Here are all the commands for the server [code]::home to go home[/code] [code]::shops for various shops[/code] [code]::ffapk for free for all pking[/code] [code]::pure for the stats listed above[/code]
No pics because my laptop cant take Screenshots
Server DL link http://uppit.com/v/42JOHPN1 Client DL link http://uppit.com/v/OWI2R5WC
The server can Be used with silabsoft and you can add your own models have fun
i build this server from scratch enjoy
